fitful -->  erratic,sporadic --> irregular, intermitente
scarce / scarcely --> lacking --> mínimamente,escaso
phlegmatic --> calmed,composed --> flemático,tranquilo
rascals --> child:mischievous --> pillo/a, mocoso/a, canalla, granuja
Teutonic --> ethno-linguistic Indo-European group of northern European origin -->  gente germánica
incontinently --> lacking control over bodily functions --> incontinente
run about --> To run haphazardly or in different directions in an area.
haphazardly--> running in a random way --> caprichosamente,anárquicamente,a voleo.
slender --> person:slim --> delgado/a
giddy --> dizzy --> mareado
keb --> miscarry / reject a lamb
exultation--> rejoicing --> exultación, júbilo
Chiefly --> mainly --> principalmente
sneered --> make a scornful expression --> mirar con desdén
scornful --> contemtuous --> despreciativo, desdeñoso/a
glistening --> shiny from wetness --> brillante, reluciente (por el agua)
bacillus --> bacterium --> bacilio

